          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1656238137014-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s] </strong>finely</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>to a bowl along with your <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and your <strong>mayo</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>remaining rice vinegar</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> cold water </strong>and a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>then mix well<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>spring onion & ginger mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1656238141455-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1656238141455-x400.jpg",
