          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1656238141455-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 20 min, remove the dish with the pulled pork from the oven and discard the <strong>tin foil</strong></p><p>Pull the <strong>pork</strong> apart using two forks and mix everything through the juices</p><p>Return the dish to the oven for 8-10 min further or until the sauce has been absorbed and the pork has started to crisp – this is your <strong>Korean-style</strong> <strong>pulled pork</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1656238145638-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
